    <item>
      <title>印度大选前预算需要注意什么</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-29/what-to-watch-out-for-in-india-s-pre-election-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理纳伦德拉·莫迪可能会利用印度选举前的最后一份预算，通过新的支出措施来吸引选民，同时避免财政赤字增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-29/what-to-watch-out-for-in-india-s-pre-election-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 03:30:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美军阵亡后拜登面临对抗伊朗的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/biden-faces-pressure-to-confront-iran-after-us-troops-killed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周末，伊朗代理人在约旦的一次无人机袭击中杀死了三名美国士兵，美国总统乔·拜登面临着与伊朗直接对抗的越来越大的压力，这恰恰冒着他试图避免的更广泛地区冲突的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/biden-faces-pressure-to-confront-iran-after-us-troops-killed</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 23:46:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马科斯推动菲律宾团结，杜特尔特猛烈抨击继任者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/marcos-calls-for-unity-as-duterte-s-son-seeks-his-resignation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯和他的前任罗德里戈·杜特尔特分别举行集会，吸引了数千名支持者，凸显了日益加深的分歧，可能会导致赢得 2022 年大选的该国最有权势的政治家族联盟的分裂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/marcos-calls-for-unity-as-duterte-s-son-seeks-his-resignation</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 16:35:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着莫迪的竞争对手变成盟友，印度的政治反对派面临打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/head-of-india-s-bihar-state-quits-to-form-new-alliance-pti-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一个挑战总理纳伦德拉·莫迪的政治联盟在全国选举前受到了打击，当时反对派控制的邦的领导人倒戈与执政党联手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/head-of-india-s-bihar-state-quits-to-form-new-alliance-pti-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 07:17:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
